ic relationships. To achieve the proposed objective, the practical use of this measuring instrument, building a Theodolite \"homemade\" was held, with low-cost materials that were available at the school. Finally, the measurements and calculations performed by the students were discussed in class, analyzing possible difficulties and knowledge acquired during the teaching-learning process.", "Data de Publicação": "2016-11-18", "url": "http://www.teses.usp.br/teses/disponiveis/55/55136/tde-18112016-191415/pt-br.php"}
